cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a technique for self-taught learning using autoencoders and sparsity constraints to select relevant source samples for improving task performance on target samples. This involves techniques related to machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural networks (cs.NE).
